23:26.277 --> 23:28.701
Here come these horses, Galpin, 30 miles an hour.

23:29.241 --> 23:31.484
Here come these people with spears and swords.

23:31.645 --> 23:35.089
You know what happens in the first 20 minutes of battle?

23:35.590 --> 23:37.132
You lose 60,000 people.

23:39.495 --> 23:40.416
Nobody wins.

23:40.437 --> 23:44.662
60,000 will go down.

23:46.024 --> 23:48.628
Read the statistics of the battles in the Old Testament.

23:48.868 --> 23:50.450
Those 20,000 were lost that day.

23:50.594 --> 23:54.803
That's 20,000 widows and 80,000 orphans in one day.

23:57.048 --> 23:58.211
That's typical warfare.

23:58.672 --> 24:00.155
Why should it be any different today?

24:00.997 --> 24:01.398
Tell me.

24:03.603 --> 24:05.166
Why should it be any different today?

24:06.309 --> 24:08.594
At the spiritual level where we sin

24:08.738 --> 24:18.733
our 200,000 young people, and I hope finishers who are over 50, and I hope retirement people who ought to be doing that instead of golfing in Arizona, go with the forces.

24:18.993 --> 24:20.976
The first 20,000 are going down.

24:21.296 --> 24:30.770
And if we are surprised at the fiery ordeal, the other 60,000 or 180,000 are coming home, no!

24:32.738 --> 24:34.680
Keep on walking into the fire.

24:35.000 --> 24:36.642
Keep on walking into the flame.

24:36.902 --> 24:38.584
Keep on walking into the prisons.

24:38.884 --> 24:40.606
Keep on walking into the swords.

24:41.587 --> 24:43.169
It's the only way it's going to get done.

24:43.589 --> 24:44.230
Paul did it.

24:44.490 --> 24:46.212
Walked into the synagogues.

24:46.272 --> 24:47.433
Walked into the prisons.

24:47.554 --> 24:52.198
Walked into the persecution over and over again.

24:52.219 --> 24:55.622
Because therein will two things happen.

24:55.642 --> 24:59.346
Christ will be magnified because He will be seen to be your gain.

25:00.322 --> 25:01.804
You walk into that situation.

25:02.004 --> 25:03.706
What about people going to explain your life?

25:06.169 --> 25:07.510
You want a nice house in the suburbs?

25:09.412 --> 25:10.434
Want to get a good job?

25:10.634 --> 25:11.635
Want to get a good wife?

25:11.735 --> 25:12.776
Want to have lots of kids?

25:12.957 --> 25:13.617
Want to get old?

25:13.637 --> 25:14.618
Want to have grandchildren?

25:14.959 --> 25:17.922
Blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah, blah.

25:17.942 --> 25:19.104
Where is Christianity?

25:19.684 --> 25:22.047
That's just American dream.

25:24.230 --> 25:28.114
Take up your cross and follow me.

25:28.738 --> 25:31.061
And it leads directly to Calvary.

25:31.362 --> 25:33.385
Let us go with him outside the camp.

25:33.405 --> 25:36.910
For here we have no lasting city and let us bear the reproach with him.

25:37.130 --> 25:39.835
The great commission won't be filled any other way.

25:39.875 --> 25:46.745
Pastors, would you please go back to your churches and begin to breed crazy people.

25:48.187 --> 25:49.869
Breed crazy people.

25:50.050 --> 25:51.292
Don't be like the pastor.

25:51.632 --> 25:52.774
I really am done here.

25:52.794 --> 25:54.997
I know my time is done.

25:55.017 --> 25:56.379
Don't be like the pastor.

25:57.000 --> 25:58.322
Now into one seminar.

25:58.914 --> 26:02.960
And I had once a high regard for this man, still do kind of, but.

26:08.128 --> 26:17.582
He said, well, when I first came here, I saw everybody had two houses, house on the lake, house home, two cars, everything.

26:17.602 --> 26:18.703
And they'd go away.

26:18.723 --> 26:25.493
And I tried for a while to preach wartime lifestyle and simplicity and radical Christianity.

26:25.533 --> 26:28.658
And finally, I said, you can't beat him.

26:30.498 --> 26:32.140
I almost walked down.

26:32.161 --> 26:33.623
My heart absolutely sucked.

26:33.643 --> 26:35.746
Brothers, I'm clean.

26:35.766 --> 26:37.749
Don't join him!

26:37.769 --> 26:38.891
Don't join him!

26:40.994 --> 26:51.850
Thank you for listening to this episode of Light and Truth, where we are committed to providing God-centered preaching to help you see Christ clearly and treasure Him truly.

26:52.451 --> 26:53.974
I'm your host, Dan Kruver.

26:54.915 --> 26:59.442
In our next episode, John Piper begins a two-part series titled

26:59.714 --> 27:01.901
the doctor's prescription for joy.

27:02.604 --> 27:03.447
I hope you'll join us.

27:04.390 --> 27:07.922
For more resources, visit desiringgod.org.

